Our Surveyor Android Application is a robust complement to our web application, what allows to create, map and manager flows based on a mobile chat in any place of the world - all you need is an Android Device charged.  Specifically, it provides a good solution to the users: 

Starts sounding or inquiries that imitates the communication flow, based on chat.
Collect data from an Android Device and send them to ilhapush when you are in an internet connection. 
Add the collected data to our serves and extract them to subsequent analyze. 
